興（《眾新聞》主筆）的文章，這些分析文章提供了政府以外的看法，這些持平的評論對香港非常重要。<br />\n<br />\n《眾新聞》於今年1月1日推出，這幾個月下來，如果你認為《眾新聞》的內容可讀，想繼續看下去，請幫忙我們完成眾籌的目標。<br />\n<br />\n我們要在6月20日達到眾籌300萬的目標，以補助我今年到年底的營運開支。我們目前已籌得超過100萬元，距離目標仍遠。你可以透過以下方法，支持我們的眾籌：<br />\n<br />\n1) 到Fringebacker眾籌平台捐款：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/supportus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Fsupportus&d=%2B4z7xIHEW9mqiOB01FK1epUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=72b73eb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkcnews.com/supportus</a><br />\n2) 新增Paypal帳戶：<a href=\"http://paypal.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaypal.hkcnews.com&d=%2B4z7xIHEW9mqiOB01FK1epUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=36ee584a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">paypal.hkcnews.com</a><br />\n3) 寄支票給經營《眾新聞》的「公民記者有限公司」（Civic Journalists Limited) ，地址：九龍長沙灣永康街77號環薈中心1210室。<br />\n4) 直接存入「公民記者有限公司」的匯豐銀行戶口：747-027688- 838<br />\n<br />\n註：用第3和第4種方法支持我們的朋友，請連同「個人電郵資料」和「存款收據副本」email到眾新聞電郵信箱info @ <a href=\"http://hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com&d=%2B4z7xIHEW9mqiOB01FK1epUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=0ead3d40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com</a>。捐款500元或以上者，可享有為期一年的每周時事通訊。通訊會在眾籌活動結束後開始寄出。"},{"pid":"1ed7e90f5a5f8a2ac59180fae1066fcb3c7dce9e","tid":262326,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:01:51.000Z","msg":"正經post冇人理？"},{"pid":"9d4f895b25375b7fc19e400f1cb7f2c2f661ba5f","tid":262326,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b841b09b377ec6c72395328ce7f843dc3fae2ff7","tid":262326,"uid":110877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T02:36:13.000Z","msg":"一早科左水"},{"pid":"0f2eb9ab6a81d038da6cfdba97d57fd20deab370","tid":262326,"uid":41992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre